00:54:04,970 --> 00:54:07,450
I had the wrong room number.

819
00:54:07,450 --> 00:54:09,110
Follow me.

820
00:54:13,950 --> 00:54:15,730
Look now.

821
00:54:18,470 --> 00:54:20,330
Dad?

822
00:54:22,550 --> 00:54:24,230
Dad.

823
00:54:24,230 --> 00:54:27,970
You're so absent-minded. You left your jacket here.

824
00:54:31,860 --> 00:54:33,860
Look, it's my dad.

825
00:54:33,860 --> 00:54:36,130
My dad!

826
00:54:36,130 --> 00:54:38,700
It's my dad!

827
00:54:38,700 --> 00:54:41,900
My dad! Guys, look. It's my dad.

828
00:54:41,900 --> 00:54:43,890
- Guys, my dad. 
 - Hello.

829
00:54:43,890 --> 00:54:45,910
My dad.

830
00:54:47,520 --> 00:54:51,050
See? It's not Kang Minju.

831
00:54:51,050 --> 00:54:53,380
Dad.

832
00:54:53,380 --> 00:54:55,690
I'm sorry.

833
00:54:55,690 --> 00:54:59,020
Nuna. Nuna, where are you going?

834
00:55:04,370 --> 00:55:06,530
Let's go. It's okay.

835
00:55:27,770 --> 00:55:29,930
I'm a bit upset.

836
00:55:30,750 --> 00:55:33,410
Never mind the others.

837
00:55:33,410 --> 00:55:36,180
I didn't expect you would doubt me.

838
00:55:36,180 --> 00:55:38,210
I'm sorry.

839
00:55:38,210 --> 00:55:41,360
I kept telling myself there's no way,

840
00:55:41,360 --> 00:55:43,740
but Yuri was so sure about it.

841
00:55:44,840 --> 00:55:47,290
I had no idea you had so little trust in me.

842
00:55:47,290 --> 00:55:50,540
If only I didn't see you with Kang Minju like that—

843
00:55:53,280 --> 00:55:57,220
What did you see me doing with Kang Minju?

844
00:55:59,830 --> 00:56:03,670
To be honest, I saw it.

845
00:56:04,660 --> 00:56:07,260
You and Kang Minju were looking at each other tenderly at the café.

846
00:56:07,260 --> 00:56:08,900
I was?

847
00:56:11,090 --> 00:56:13,700
Oh, that was nothing.

848
00:56:13,700 --> 00:56:16,520
I knew you would say that.

849
00:56:16,520 --> 00:56:19,310
That's why I didn't want to bring it up.

850
00:56:22,850 --> 00:56:24,590
I'm sorry.

851
00:56:24,590 --> 00:56:27,060
But it's really nothing.

852
00:56:27,060 --> 00:56:30,270
She's nothing more than a junior.

853
00:56:30,270 --> 00:56:32,580
I'll keep my eyes on you.

854
00:56:35,710 --> 00:56:37,450
Bye.

855
00:56:41,590 --> 00:56:43,500
But...

856
00:56:43,500 --> 00:56:45,810
I also have something to tell you.

857
00:56:47,030 --> 00:56:52,280
It wasn't fun watching you and Yuri kiss.

858
00:56:52,280 --> 00:56:54,220
That wasn't a kiss.

859
00:56:54,220 --> 00:56:56,390
That was just one second—

860
00:56:58,260 --> 00:57:00,140
Three seconds?

861
00:57:04,780 --> 00:57:06,740
I'm sorry.

862
00:57:06,740 --> 00:57:09,540
From now on, I'll draw a clearer line.

863
00:57:10,310 --> 00:57:12,400
I'll keep my eyes on you.

864
00:57:13,470 --> 00:57:14,680
Go in.

865
00:57:14,680 --> 00:57:17,430
♫  I see your eyes  ♫

866
00:57:18,380 --> 00:57:22,030
♫  Even the tears filled to the brim  ♫

867
00:57:22,030 --> 00:57:25,050
♫  Will be no more  ♫

868
00:57:25,050 --> 00:57:29,310
♫  So, believe me now  ♫

869
00:57:29,310 --> 00:57:32,400
♫  Open your eyes  ♫

870
00:57:42,110 --> 00:57:44,960
You scared me. Why are you here, Dad?

871
00:57:44,960 --> 00:57:48,190
Why do you look like this?

872
00:57:48,190 --> 00:57:52,170
Your mom said to come home right away.

873
00:57:52,170 --> 00:57:53,290
Looking like this?

874
00:57:53,290 --> 00:57:55,960
All can be forgiven if you're cute.

875
00:57:58,200 --> 00:58:01,590
Not true. You're not cute at all.

876
00:58:01,590 --> 00:58:05,070
I feel like Mom will ask you for a divorce.

877
00:58:42,080 --> 00:58:44,370
Iljo!

878
00:58:47,590 --> 00:58:50,490
Gosh, seriously.

879
00:59:16,680 --> 00:59:21,050
Park Yunjae. What brings you here so early?

880
00:59:21,050 --> 00:59:23,780
What's with that on your head?

881
00:59:39,190 --> 00:59:41,690
What is this?

882
00:59:44,100 --> 00:59:45,880
Want to try it together?

883
00:59:45,880 --> 00:59:48,550
Lift your leg like this. Lift your leg and kick.

884
00:59:52,320 --> 00:59:55,360
Link arms and spin, spin.

885
00:59:57,150 --> 00:59:59,220
Spin. Spin.

886
00:59:59,220 --> 01:00:02,180
♫  Make scar, make scars on my heart?  ♫

887
01:00:02,180 --> 01:00:05,100
♫  Unable to leave, again like this  ♫

888
01:00:05,100 --> 01:00:11,370
♫  I wander around you  ♫

889
01:00:11,370 --> 01:00:13,190
One more time. Okay.

890
01:00:13,190 --> 01:00:15,170
One, two.

891
01:00:19,750 --> 01:00:24,060
♫  Can't stop, can't stop thinking about you  ♫

892
01:00:27,370 --> 01:00:30,200
What are you two doing here so early?

893
01:00:30,200 --> 01:00:34,240
Minju, what about you? What brings you here so early?

894
01:00:34,240 --> 01:00:36,650
Me? I'm moving in.

895
01:00:36,650 --> 01:00:38,250
Moving in?

896
01:00:38,250 --> 01:00:39,870
Where?

897
01:00:39,870 --> 01:00:41,530
Here.

898
01:00:43,650 --> 01:00:45,750
Here?

899
01:00:45,750 --> 01:00:47,190
This building?

900
01:00:47,190 --> 01:00:50,600
Yes. Second floor, unit 202.

