01:01:15,300 --> 01:01:23,740
♫  You taught me how to feel with every word  ♫

904
01:01:23,740 --> 01:01:29,560
♫  And every glance we've been through  ♫

905
01:01:29,560 --> 01:01:33,470
♫  It will always be the same  ♫

